given what's going on, but...

37:28.594 --> 37:32.250
I begged the manager to let
my band play one more night.

37:32.250 --> 37:34.469
Gonna need a singer.

37:34.469 --> 37:36.079
Come on, you deserve
to be up on that stage.

37:36.079 --> 37:37.820
No, no, no, no, no--

37:37.820 --> 37:40.214
Even if it is
just one night only.

37:40.214 --> 37:43.870
